text: Lovely staff, well made coffee, fair prices

The best Starbucks in Singapore I ever been. Dropped a drink on floor, was gonna buy a new one but the barista made me a new one for free.
This made my day. ❤️

I ordered a Java Chip Frappuchino, and was served a watery / melted coffee? I've ordered Frappuchino from many other branches before, and this is the first time I've received a Frappuchino like that. It looked like the Frappuchino had been sitting out for some time, and even had a weird aftertaste.
Best prices in SG with comfy environment and aesthetically appealing surroundings. Only open during weekdays till 7pm
Ordered a tea latte, given tea only, ask for a remake, but got a diluted latte, what kind of quality control is this?!
